-- Basel Group Publishes Rules on Banks’ Disclosure of Capital
-- B y   J i m   B r u n s d e n
-- 2012-06-26T07:30:10Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-26/basel-group-publishes-rules-on-banks-disclosure-of-capital.html
Global financial regulators released
rules on the information banks should publish about their
capital levels so that investors aren’t misled.  The  Basel Committee on Banking Supervision , which brings
together supervisors from 27 nations including the U.S., the
U.K. and China, published the rules today on its  website .  -- Editor: Jones Hayden  To contact the reporters on this story:
Jim Brunsden in Brussels at 
 jbrunsden@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Anthony Aarons at   aaarons@bloomberg.net  